    {
      "parameters": {
        "authentication": "webhook",
        "content": "=# ❌ AWS LEARNING CLUB POLAR\n## ⚠️ EVENT CANCELLATION NOTICE\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n# 📢 {{ $('If').item.json[' Event Name'] }}\n\nHello @everyone,\n\nWe regret to inform you that the following event has been **cancelled**.\n\n```ansi\n\u001b[1;31m🔴 STATUS: CANCELLED\u001b[0m\n```\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n📅 Originally Scheduled\n> {{ $('If').item.json.date }}\n\n🕒 Time\n>  {{ $('If').item.json.startTime }} – {{ $('If').item.json.endTime }}\n📍 Venue\n>{{ $('If').item.json.Venue }}\n🎤 Speaker\n> {{ $('If').item.json.Speaker }}\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n### ❗ Important Notice\n\nDue to unforeseen circumstances, **{{ $('If').item.json[' Event Name'] }}** will no longer take place as scheduled.\n\nWe sincerely apologize for the inconvenience and appreciate your understanding. If the event is rescheduled, an official announcement will be posted in this channel.\n\nPlease stay tuned for future updates from **AWS Learning Club POLAR**. ❄️\n\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n📅 **Cancellation Issued**\n> {{ $now.setZone(\"Asia/Manila\").toFormat(\"cccc, MMMM d, yyyy • h:mm a\") }}\n\n🆔 Tracking ID\n{{ $('If').item.json['Event ID'] }}\n\nThank you for your patience and continued support.",
        "options": {}
      },
