        "content": "=🛠️  **INTERNAL LOG: NEW DRAFT EVENT CREATED**  🛠️\n======================================================\n\n👤  CREATED BY: {{ $json['Created By'] }}\n📝  EVENT TITLE: {{ $json[' Event Name'] }}\n\n------------------------------------------------------\nℹ️  This event is currently in Draft status. No public announcements have been sent out. To push this live to the club channel, change the spreadsheet dropdown status flag to \"Scheduled\".*\n\n🆔  *System ID: {{ $json['Event ID'] }}\n\nTo change status, go to Google Sheet Link \n[INSERT YOUR GOOGLE SHEET SHARE LINK HERE]\n======================================================\n",
        "options": {}
